    "data": [
        {
            "title": "大埔唐樓變身釣魚機賭檔  警拘11人檢$2000賭款",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/21de83fd4df81273ff2c5d1339d58ea3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022006320819562.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大埔警區反三合會行動組人員根據線報及經深入調查後，今日（20日）凌晨約一時展開反非法賭博行動，突擊搜查大埔懷仁街的一個唐樓單位，搗破一個懷疑非法釣魚機賭檔。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，一名44歲姓許本地男子懷疑為該賭檔主持人，涉嫌「經營賭博場所」被捕。另外，該單位內共有八名本地男子及兩名本地女子，年齡介乎28至67歲，則涉嫌「在賭博場所內賭博」被捕。所有被捕人現正被扣留調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091913/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/689e006ea140a42e4357e609c1755c3d/2025-02/a_1__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>人員於行動中共檢獲四部釣魚機、一批遊戲卡、一批賭具及約二千元賭款。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據香港法例第148章《賭博條例》，任何人經營或協助經營非法賭場，一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款500萬及監禁7年。而任何人士在賭場內賭博，亦屬違法，首次定罪，可被判處罰款3萬及監禁9個月。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053815/即時-港聞-大埔唐樓變身釣魚機賭檔-警拘11人檢-2000賭款",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 06:41:38",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天文台｜日間短暫時間有陽光 最高氣溫約20度 吹和緩至清勁偏東風",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5c58a9d1351c82052c2029123a05b479/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022006223557059.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股清勁至強風程度的東北季候風正影響廣東沿岸。同時，一道雲帶覆蓋該區。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲。日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。吹和緩至清勁偏東風，初時離岸及高地間中吹強風。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091907/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35e3aa26363cc33e138395cf7d391255/2025-02/14_14.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091911/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d9b069b7eac1d74c2688f180c7b70f2/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-19_at_10_21_07_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091908/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32996a6e4125a9709ed199bf0f52377f/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-19_at_10_16_50_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091909/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a933f27b86fae34ca21b8a5c6cb4ce9b/2025-02/13_15.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091910/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d93be12e5a572a87da4a35df12d557a/2025-02/11_15.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展望未來一兩日風勢仍然較大，部分時間有陽光。星期日漸轉吹偏北風，稍後氣溫下降，星期一早上相當清涼。下週中期雲量增多，氣溫稍為回升。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053814/即時-港聞-天文台-日間短暫時間有陽光-最高氣溫約20度-吹和緩至清勁偏東風",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 06:31:42",
